Whoa, this is the big one! We spent the last few months getting feedback directly from you and rebuilt the app. We believe you will find the new app to be your goto mobile marketplace.
Highlights:
* New design and homepage with more intuitive browsing
* Inbox for all messages, in one place
* Simple shipping: USPS is the only Mercari-tracked option
* Saved Search is back!
* And many more
Our biggest goal was to rebuild the app to allow the faster release of new features. Stay tuned for more significant updates!

What’s New:
A picture is worth a thousand words, and we’ve made it easier to post multiple pictures for each item.
* You can now upload 4 photos at once. Your most popular request, now delivered. 
* Optimized search filters that are also easier on the eyes (thanks to our rockin’ design team)
* More bugs crushed. Thanks so much for your reports, they’ve helped immensely in our bug eradication efforts!

In this release, we’re introducing a highly requested feature!
 
Use our Make an Offer feature to quickly and easily negotiate the price of an item. It’s a streamlined system built into Private Chat that will lead to simple communications and fast sales!

Make an Offer allows you to easily:
- Make offers
- Review offers and make counteroffers
- Accept offers for immediate sales

We also swept out a few more bugs, and tuned the app for better performance.

Keep the feedback coming, we’re listening!

Minor UI improvements to make your buy and sell experience more enjoyable than ever.

In this release, we improved the way you post an item.
- Hashtags! – Tag your items to make them easier for buyers to find.
- Required Item Descriptions – Items sell faster when they're well-described. Give it a try.
- Image Cropping – This feature is back and working as expected. Now it's not  a croppy experience!

And as always, bugs were squashed and performance was improved. Keep the feedback coming—we’re listening and working on your suggestions.

In this release, we’ve made it easier to find an item.
- New Filters – We improved the way you sort your search results.
- My Sizes – We’ll remember the size you searched for last time… because we care.
- Delete Photos – Exactly what it sounds like… delete photos you don’t want!

And as always, bugs were squashed and performance was improved. Keep the feedback coming—we’re listening and working on your suggestions.

In this release, we want to help you search and sell.

Sold Filter – We brought it back! Search Sold items to help you set your price. 

And as always, bugs were squashed and performance was improved. Keep the feedback coming—we’re listening and working on your suggestions.

In this release, we’ve focused on listing items.
- Like List – See which users liked your items (and message them to make a sale).
- Suggest New Listings – After you create a new listing, we’ll suggest similar items to sell.
- Category Detail – We’ve added categories back into the item details. Did you miss them?
- iOS Optimization – Now we play nice with iOS 11!

And as always, bugs were squashed and performance was improved. Keep the feedback coming—we’re listening and working on your suggestions.

In this release, we focused on making Mercari more helpful. 

Title Autocomplete – We’ll recommend a title for your listing. Dawww, look at us finishing your sentences.

Missing Fields – If you miss a required field, we’ll point it out for you.

Saved Search – A little bird told us you’d like to see newest posts. You got it!

Apple Pay - We've added another easy way to pay, the Apple way!

And as always, bugs were squashed and performance was improved. Keep the feedback coming—we’re listening and working on your suggestions.

In this release, we’ve made shipping even easier!
- FedEx SmartPost – We’ve reintroduced this Economy option; save up to $5 per shipment.
- Guess Your (Shipping) Weight – Our UI now defaults to the most likely weight class.
- USPS Weight Rates – The lowest $4 fixed-rate label now covers up to 1 lb! Pay $7 for 1–3 lbs.

And as always, bugs were squashed and performance was improved. Keep the feedback coming—we’re listening and working on your suggestions.

In this release, we focused on selling and safety.

New Home Screen – We’re your selling app, and now we look like it. Our redesigned home screen shows what sold recently and surfaces ideas for new listings.

In-app Identity Verification – Knowing who we’re doing business with keeps everyone safer. We’ve integrated an easy, more secure way to verify someone’s identity.
